modName: Thalmor Influence - No shrine of Talos in Whiterun
summary: Changes Whiterun's Shrine of Talos to an improvised Shrine of Akatosh.
descriptionHtml:
V1.1:
-Heimskr is back
-Better model for the shrine

Description:
I always thought it was silly that the thalmor didn't care about the Shrine of talos in Whiterun.
This mod Changes the shrine of Talos in Whiterun into an improvised shrine of Akatosh
The mod removed Heimskr before, butI decided to bring back Heimskr
because he actually gives more immersion rather than takes away.

I am willing to do a series of Thalmor Influence mods.
Feel free to make mod requests.

A new Thalmor Influence mod is out!: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59022/?
author: gtantsa
